  {
   "start": 493.84,
   "end": 494.1,
   "text": "Boom,"
  },
  {
   "start": 494.14,
   "end": 494.58,
   "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
   "start": 496.3,
   "end": 496.72,
   "text": "Um,"
  },
  {
   "start": 497.34,
   "end": 498.42,
   "text": "That's,"
  },
  {
   "start": 498.5,
   "end": 498.78,
   "text": "That's,"
  },
  {
   "start": 498.82,
   "end": 500.24,
   "text": "That's basically my soul argument."
  },
  {
   "start": 500.82,
   "end": 501.1,
   "text": "See,"
  },
  {
   "start": 501.1,
   "end": 503.58,
   "text": "If it's a crime to abort somebody,"
  },
  {
   "start": 504.0,
   "end": 505.1,
   "text": "There has to be a victim."
  },
  {
   "start": 505.48,
   "end": 506.62,
   "text": "That's what a crime is."
  },
  {
   "start": 506.98,
   "end": 509.42,
   "text": "A crime is perpetrating something against somebody"
  },
  {
   "start": 509.42,
   "end": 511.54,
   "text": "Who suffers for it."
  },
  {
   "start": 512.88,
   "end": 514.62,
   "text": "Victimless crime isn't a crime,"
  },
  {
   "start": 515.0,
   "end": 515.32,
   "text": "You know."
  },
  {
   "start": 515.86,
   "end": 518.64,
   "text": "Like it's illegal to have oral sex in 13 states."
  },
  {
   "start": 519.32,
   "end": 519.68,
   "text": "Is that a,"
  },
  {
   "start": 519.74,
   "end": 522.62,
   "text": "So does that mean it's a crime to have oral sex in,"
  },
  {
   "start": 522.74,
   "end": 523.82,
   "text": "In those states?"
  },
  {
   "start": 524.36,
   "end": 524.76,
   "text": "Technically,"
  },
  {
   "start": 525.4,
   "end": 526.4,
   "text": "But it doesn't mean it's,"
  },
  {
   "start": 526.54,
   "end": 527.5,
   "text": "It should be a crime."
  },
  {
   "start": 527.5,
   "end": 529.88,
   "text": "Somebody should strike that out of the law books."
  },
  {
   "start": 530.38,
   "end": 536.16,
   "text": "It was illegal for a black person to drink out of a white person water fountain 50 years ago."
  },
  {
   "start": 537.38,
   "end": 537.74,
   "text": "Technically,"
  },
  {
   "start": 537.96,
   "end": 538.18,
   "text": "Yes,"
  },
  {
   "start": 538.22,
   "end": 538.86,
   "text": "That was a crime."
  },
  {
   "start": 539.08,
   "end": 540.24,
   "text": "But was it really a crime?"
  },
  {
   "start": 540.84,
   "end": 541.12,
   "text": "No,"
  },
  {
   "start": 541.16,
   "end": 542.12,
   "text": "It wasn't really a crime."
  },
  {
   "start": 542.3,
   "end": 542.88,
   "text": "Common sense,"
  },
  {
   "start": 542.96,
   "end": 543.5,
   "text": "It wasn't a crime."
  },
  {
   "start": 544.38,
   "end": 545.96,
   "text": "So if you make abortion legal,"
  },
  {
   "start": 546.06,
   "end": 546.4,
   "text": "Illegal,"
  },
  {
   "start": 546.92,
   "end": 548.68,
   "text": "And you say it's a crime to abort a fetus,"
  },
  {
   "start": 549.14,
   "end": 550.08,
   "text": "It'd be the same thing."
  },
  {
   "start": 551.42,
   "end": 551.78,
   "text": "Technically,"
  },
  {
   "start": 552.0,
   "end": 553.06,
   "text": "It would be a crime,"
  },
  {
   "start": 553.14,
   "end": 553.72,
   "text": "But in reality,"
  },
  {
   "start": 553.82,
   "end": 554.4,
   "text": "Would it be a crime?"
  },
  {
   "start": 554.4,
   "end": 554.62,
   "text": "No,"
  },
  {
   "start": 554.68,
   "end": 555.98,
   "text": "Because there's no victim involved."
  },
  {
   "start": 556.08,
   "end": 557.24,
   "text": "It's a victimless crime."
  },
  {
   "start": 558.06,
   "end": 559.36,
   "text": "The baby is not a victim."
  },
  {
   "start": 560.08,
   "end": 562.88,
   "text": "The baby is a sack of meat,"
  },
  {
   "start": 563.28,
   "end": 565.5,
   "text": "And the soul that was going to inhabit it"
  },
  {
   "start": 565.5,
   "end": 568.64,
   "text": "Is just going to pass on to the next,"
  },
  {
   "start": 568.72,
   "end": 571.76,
   "text": "To the next girl who's about to have a baby."
  },
  {
   "start": 571.86,
   "end": 571.98,
   "text": "Well,"
  },
  {
   "start": 571.98,
   "end": 572.54,
   "text": "Then you may go,"
  },
  {
   "start": 572.74,
   "end": 572.76,
   "text": "Oh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 572.76,
   "end": 573.36,
   "text": "But they're going to get,"
  },
  {
   "start": 573.44,
   "end": 575.56,
   "text": "They're going to get stacked up."
  },
  {
   "start": 575.6,
   "end": 577.08,
   "text": "It's going to become a whole traffic jam."
  },
  {
   "start": 577.44,
   "end": 578.72,
   "text": "If you abort all these people,"
  },
  {
   "start": 578.82,
   "end": 579.76,
   "text": "Then how are you going to be,"
  },
  {
   "start": 580.18,
   "end": 581.38,
   "text": "How are there going to be enough,"
  },
  {
   "start": 581.48,
   "end": 581.82,
   "text": "You know,"
  },
  {
   "start": 581.88,
   "end": 584.02,
   "text": "Bodies for all the souls who want to get born into people?"
  },
  {
   "start": 584.4,
   "end": 584.82,
   "text": "Well,"
  },
  {
   "start": 584.88,
   "end": 589.9,
   "text": "Why don't you say that to the six billion souls who are alive today that weren't alive 200 years ago?"
  },
  {
   "start": 591.06,
   "end": 593.68,
   "text": "We have too many people in the world as it is."
  },
  {
   "start": 594.78,
   "end": 598.02,
   "text": "And then those souls will always have somebody to be born in."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.1,
   "end": 601.5,
   "text": "Go and go be born on another planet somewhere or another parallel universe."
  },
  {
   "start": 601.62,
   "end": 602.14,
   "text": "Who cares?"
  },
  {
   "start": 604.18,
   "end": 605.4,
   "text": "But the fact of the matter,"
  },
  {
   "start": 605.44,
   "end": 606.14,
   "text": "And I'm out of time,"
  },
  {
   "start": 606.36,
   "end": 609.56,
   "text": "Is that a crime is only a crime if there's a victim involved."
  },
  {
   "start": 609.56,
   "end": 611.6,
   "text": "And so the soul doesn't matter,"
  },
  {
   "start": 611.78,
   "end": 612.3,
   "text": "Doesn't care."
  },
  {
   "start": 613.1,
